。盡沽離場❗</title><updated>2025-05-11T12:08:03+08:00</updated><author><name>精神裁判</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-11T12:08:03+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572352570"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572352570"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16215662" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572352570" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250511/20250511_bbc43d1c543ad1310f15M2wLWWD9StZW.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/48d840/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250511/20250511_bbc43d1c543ad1310f15M2wLWWD9StZW.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16215662_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16215662&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IMG-20250511-WA0081.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (175.19 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-5-11 12:08&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31924230&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=173226257568202a8af30768_15176547"/><published>2025-05-11T12:08:03+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>25176704854c5ecaaf6a9612b60e76ca</id><title>特朗普：中美經貿會談取巨大進展</title><updated>2025-05-11T12:33:34+08:00</updated><author><name>onine仔</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-11T12:33:34+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572352910"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572352910"&gt;中美高層經貿會談上周六（10日）在瑞士日內瓦完成首日談判，美國總統特朗普在社交平台Truth Social發文指中美進行了一次非常好的會晤，雙方以友好及建設性的方式協商全面重設美中貿易關係，達成很多共識。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;特朗普還指，為了中美兩國的利益，美方希望看到中國向美國企業開放，「取得了巨大進展！！！」。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原文網址：特朗普：中美經貿會談取巨大進展 | on.cc東網 | 中港台&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20250511/bkn-20250511081235557-0511_00822_001.html" target="_blank" uhash="b4270cf5b9d1bd3bac2079c90e14efb2"&gt;https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20250511/bkn-20250511081235557-0511_00822_001.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572352910" original-img="https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20250511/photo/bkn-20250511081235557-0511_00822_001_01p.jpg?20250511102640"&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20250511/photo/bkn-20250511081235557-0511_00822_001_01p.jpg?20250511102640" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/e91551/f/800x0/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20250511/photo/bkn-20250511081235557-0511_00822_001_01p.jpg?20250511102640"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31924255&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=173226257568202a8af30768_15176547"/><published>2025-05-11T12:33:34+08:00</published></entry></feed>